Let me with you patience adde one place more, of many others, to cloſe up this,Zach. 12.16. 1 Kings 22.20. Revel 9.1, 2, 3. Mich. 2.6, 11. They ſtraightned the Spirit of the Lord and ſilenced his Prophets, they liked not their Prophecies which never boded unto them any good, but ſtill, as they thought, put them to ſhame; therefore to fit their humour, that there might be like Prieſt like people;
